---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact
description: "Write to me — contact form. I reply to messages about creativity, technology, and collaboration."
lang: en
pageType: page
permalink: /en/contact/
pair: /kontakt/
---
<div class="essay-head">
  <h1>Contact</h1>
</div>
<article>
  <p>The fastest way to reach me is <a href="{{ site.links.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a>. If you prefer the longer form — write here and the message lands straight in my inbox.</p>
</article>
<form class="contact-form" action="https://formsubmit.co/contact@arturpaprocki.com" method="POST">
  <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Message from arturpaprocki.com">
  <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="{{ site.publicUrl }}/en/thank-you/">
  <input type="text" name="_honey" class="hp" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true">
  <label for="cf-name">Name</label>
  <input id="cf-name" type="text" name="name" required autocomplete="name">
  <label for="cf-email">Your e-mail</label>
  <input id="cf-email" type="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email">
  <label for="cf-message">Message</label>
  <textarea id="cf-message" name="message" rows="7" required></textarea>
  <button class="btn" type="submit">
    <span class="flourish">{% gesture "frame", 240, 60 %}</span>
    Send message
  </button>
</form>
